        <!-- Company Story -->
        <div>
          <h4 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">Our Story</h4>
          <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed mb-4">
            Based in the Greater Toronto Area, our team combines deep technical knowledge with real-world business experience to deliver solutions that drive measurable results. We specialize in transforming business operations through expert Microsoft Dynamics 365 Business Central implementations and cutting-edge AI integration.
          </p>
          <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
            Our proven track record spans pharmaceutical, manufacturing, logistics, and financial industries, with a consistent focus on delivering 60-90% efficiency improvements for our clients.
          </p>
        </div>
